---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About | Draconis Systems"
  description="Draconis Systems builds workload-focused custom PCs with validated thermals and stability-first engineering."
  breadcrumbs={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "About" }]}
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid grid-2">
      <article class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1>Engineering-first custom PC company.</h1>
        <p>
          Draconis Systems is a UK-based custom PC building company focused on measurable outcomes: frame consistency,
          render throughput, reliability, and serviceability.
        </p>
        <p>
          We prioritise compatibility discipline, clean thermal behaviour, and clear scope communication before any build is approved.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>Operating Principles</h2>
        <ul class="clean stack">
          <li>Workload-driven component selection.</li>
          <li>Compatibility and thermals validated before delivery.</li>
          <li>Transparent quote boundaries and lead times.</li>
          <li>Documentation and support path after handoff.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
